        I build cool stuff with the help of AI. Here's a peek into what I'm working on.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Newsletter Signup -->
    <div class="relative py-8 sm:py-16 mb-16 sm:mb-24 min-h-[300px] overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background wrapper with brushstroke -->
